narello-dogma-xc-hardtail-world-champs-short-track-pro-bike-check-nds-chainstay-tire-clearance-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcock-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtail-world-champs-short-track-pro-bike-check-nds-chainstay-tire-clearance.jpg 1600w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>At 170 cm tall (5ft 7″), Tom is riding the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/pinarello-dogma-xc-ht-hardtail-carbon-cross-country-mountain-bike/\" target=\"_blank\">Pinarello Dogma XC Hardtail</a> in a size small. The bike is not yet in production, and we are still waiting on Pinarello for more information about sizing availability and geometry. What we do know, is that they have implemented a patented asymmetric rear triangle design which reinforces the non-driveside with a more direct triangulated layout to offer increased stiffness to “counterbalance the higher forces being applied” through the drivetrain by the rider’s pedaling input. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcock-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtail-world-champs-short-track-pro-bike-check-sr-suntour-axon-34-tact-suspension-fork.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcock-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtail-world-champs-short-track-pro-bike-check-sr-suntour-axon-34-tact-suspension-fork-800x1200.jpg\" alt=\"tom pidcock pro bike check pinarello dogma xc hardtail sr suntour axon 34 fork tact electronic suspension damping\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcock-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtail-world-champs-short-track-pro-bike-check-sr-suntour-axon-34-tact-suspension-fork-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcock-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtail-world-champs-short-track-pro-bike-check-sr-suntour-axon-34-tact-suspension-fork-200x300.jpg 200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcock-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtail-world-champs-short-track-pro-bike-check-sr-suntour-axon-34-tact-suspension-fork-80x120.jpg 80w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcock-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtail-world-champs-short-track-pro-bike-check-sr-suntour-axon-34-tact-suspension-fork-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcock-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtail-world-champs-short-track-pro-bike-check-sr-suntour-axon-34-tact-suspension-fork-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcock-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtail-world-champs-short-track-pro-bike-check-sr-suntour-axon-34-tact-suspension-fork-1365x2048.jpg 1365w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcock-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtail-world-champs-short-track-pro-bike-check-sr-suntour-axon-34-tact-suspension-fork.jpg 1600w\" /></a><figcaption>100mm travel SR Suntour Axon 34 fork</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcock-pro-bike-check-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtai-sr-suntour-tact-electronic-suspension-dampingl.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"534\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcock-pro-bike-check-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtai-sr-suntour-tact-electronic-suspension-dampingl-800x534.jpg\" alt srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcock-pro-bike-check-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtai-sr-suntour-tact-electronic-suspension-dampingl-800x534.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcock-pro-bike-check-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtai-sr-suntour-tact-electronic-suspension-dampingl-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcock-pro-bike-check-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtai-sr-suntour-tact-electronic-suspension-dampingl-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcock-pro-bike-check-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtai-sr-suntour-tact-electronic-suspension-dampingl-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcock-pro-bike-check-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtai-sr-suntour-tact-electronic-suspension-dampingl-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcock-pro-bike-check-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtai-sr-suntour-tact-electronic-suspension-dampingl-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcock-pro-bike-check-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtai-sr-suntour-tact-electronic-suspension-dampingl.jpg 1600w\" /></a><figcaption>An electronically-actuated damper</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcock-pro-bike-check-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtail-mtb-downtube-bosses.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"534\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcock-pro-bike-check-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtail-mtb-downtube-bosses-800x534.jpg\" alt srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcock-pro-bike-check-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtail-mtb-downtube-bosses-800x534.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcock-pro-bike-check-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtail-mtb-downtube-bosses-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcock-pro-bike-check-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtail-mtb-downtube-bosses-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcock-pro-bike-check-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtail-mtb-downtube-bosses-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcock-pro-bike-check-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtail-mtb-downtube-bosses-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcock-pro-bike-check-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtail-mtb-downtube-bosses-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcock-pro-bike-check-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtail-mtb-downtube-bosses.jpg 1600w\" /></a><figcaption>TACT battery is bolted to the inside of the downtube</figcaption></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Indeed, Pidcock’s race bike is fronted by a 100mm travel SR Suntour Axon 34 fork with the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/pinarello-dogma-xc-olympic-mountain-bike/\" target=\"_blank\">TACT</a> electronic, automatic adjusting suspension damping technology. It offers up to 8 settings that vary from the ultra comfortable, to a much firmer, pedal-efficient setting. Unfortunately, mechanic Arune was not prepared to share Tom’s exact settings with us. It is not clear whether or not any production model will come with the SR Suntour electronic suspension we see on Tom’s bike.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidocks-pinareelo-dogma-xc-hardtail-race-bike-check-p1-race-technologies-singularis-m30-carbon-wheels-with-non-plus-hubs.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidocks-pinareelo-dogma-xc-hardtail-race-bike-check-p1-race-technologies-singularis-m30-carbon-wheels-with-non-plus-hubs-800x1200.jpg\" alt=\"tom pidcock pro bike check pinarello dogma xc hardtail continental race king tires\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidocks-pinareelo-dogma-xc-hardtail-race-bike-check-p1-race-technologies-singularis-m30-carbon-wheels-with-non-plus-hubs-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidocks-pinareelo-dogma-xc-hardtail-race-bike-check-p1-race-technologies-singularis-m30-carbon-wheels-with-non-plus-hubs-200x300.jpg 200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidocks-pinareelo-dogma-xc-hardtail-race-bike-check-p1-race-technologies-singularis-m30-carbon-wheels-with-non-plus-hubs-80x120.jpg 80w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidocks-pinareelo-dogma-xc-hardtail-race-bike-check-p1-race-technologies-singularis-m30-carbon-wheels-with-non-plus-hubs-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidocks-pinareelo-dogma-xc-hardtail-race-bike-check-p1-race-technologies-singularis-m30-carbon-wheels-with-non-plus-hubs-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidocks-pinareelo-dogma-xc-hardtail-race-bike-check-p1-race-technologies-singularis-m30-carbon-wheels-with-non-plus-hubs-1365x2048.jpg 1365w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidocks-pinareelo-dogma-xc-hardtail-race-bike-check-p1-race-technologies-singularis-m30-carbon-wheels-with-non-plus-hubs.jpg 1600w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Tom’s Pinarello rolls on the P1 Race Technologies Singularis M30 Wheelset with 30mm internal width carbon rims. With 24 bladed, J-bend spokes, the wavy rim is laced to a very lightweight hubset from Non Plus. Seated onto those rims is a set of 29″ x 2.3″ Continental Race King Race Sport tires with the Black Chilli Compound.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcok-pro-bike-check-2023-uci-world-champs-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtail-vertical-helium-dropper-seat-post-60mm.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcok-pro-bike-check-2023-uci-world-champs-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtail-vertical-helium-dropper-seat-post-60mm-800x1200.jpg\" alt=\"tom pidcok pro bike check 2023 uci world champs pinarello dogma xc hardtail vertical helium dropper post 60mm drop world's lightest\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcok-pro-bike-check-2023-uci-world-champs-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtail-vertical-helium-dropper-seat-post-60mm-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcok-pro-bike-check-2023-uci-world-champs-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtail-vertical-helium-dropper-seat-post-60mm-200x300.jpg 200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcok-pro-bike-check-2023-uci-world-champs-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtail-vertical-helium-dropper-seat-post-60mm-80x120.jpg 80w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcok-pro-bike-check-2023-uci-world-champs-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtail-vertical-helium-dropper-seat-post-60mm-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcok-pro-bike-check-2023-uci-world-champs-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtail-vertical-helium-dropper-seat-post-60mm-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcok-pro-bike-check-2023-uci-world-champs-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtail-vertical-helium-dropper-seat-post-60mm-1365x2048.jpg 1365w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcok-pro-bike-check-2023-uci-world-champs-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtail-vertical-helium-dropper-seat-post-60mm.jpg 1600w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>While New Zealand’s Anton Cooper chose to forgo use of a dropper seat post on his Trek Procaliber short track bike, Tom is running the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/vertical-helium-dropper-seat-post-worlds-lightest/\" target=\"_blank\">Vertical Helium Dropper Seat Post</a> – which is, incidentally, one of the world’s lightest. This one is normally an 80mm drop, but on Tom’s bike it has been limited 60mm. Atop it is a Fizik Antares saddle with carbon rails.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcok-pro-bike-check-2023-uci-world-champs-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtail-fizik-antares-saddle-carbon-rails.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"534\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcok-pro-bike-check-2023-uci-world-champs-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtail-fizik-antares-saddle-carbon-rails-800x534.jpg\" alt srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcok-pro-bike-check-2023-uci-world-champs-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtail-fizik-antares-saddle-carbon-rails-800x534.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcok-pro-bike-check-2023-uci-world-champs-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtail-fizik-antares-saddle-carbon-rails-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcok-pro-bike-check-2023-uci-world-champs-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtail-fizik-antares-saddle-carbon-rails-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcok-pro-bike-check-2023-uci-world-champs-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtail-fizik-antares-saddle-carbon-rails-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcok-pro-bike-check-2023-uci-world-champs-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtail-fizik-antares-saddle-carbon-rails-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcok-pro-bike-check-2023-uci-world-champs-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtail-fizik-antares-saddle-carbon-rails-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcok-pro-bike-check-2023-uci-world-champs-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtail-fizik-antares-saddle-carbon-rails.jpg 1600w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>In the drivetrain department, Tom runs an 11-45T cassette with a Shimano XTR short-cage derailleur. That’s paired with a Shimano XTR crankset with 170mm cranks, 38T chainring and Shimano XTR pedals. Tom rides and races with the SRM spider-based power meter.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcok-pro-bike-check-2023-uci-world-champs-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtail-shimano-xtr-cranks-srm-spider-based-power-meter.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"534\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcok-pro-bike-check-2023-uci-world-champs-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtail-shimano-xtr-cranks-srm-spider-based-power-meter-800x534.jpg\" alt srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcok-pro-bike-check-2023-uci-world-champs-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtail-shimano-xtr-cranks-srm-spider-based-power-meter-800x534.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcok-pro-bike-check-2023-uci-world-champs-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtail-shimano-xtr-cranks-srm-spider-based-power-meter-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcok-pro-bike-check-2023-uci-world-champs-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtail-shimano-xtr-cranks-srm-spider-based-power-meter-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcok-pro-bike-check-2023-uci-world-champs-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtail-shimano-xtr-cranks-srm-spider-based-power-meter-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcok-pro-bike-check-2023-uci-world-champs-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtail-shimano-xtr-cranks-srm-spider-based-power-meter-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcok-pro-bike-check-2023-uci-world-champs-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtail-shimano-xtr-cranks-srm-spider-based-power-meter-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcok-pro-bike-check-2023-uci-world-champs-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtail-shimano-xtr-cranks-srm-spider-based-power-meter.jpg 1600w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcok-pro-bike-check-2023-uci-world-champs-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtail-shimano-xtr-drivetrain-10-45-short-cage-derailleur.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcok-pro-bike-check-2023-uci-world-champs-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtail-shimano-xtr-drivetrain-10-45-short-cage-derailleur-800x1200.jpg\" alt srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcok-pro-bike-check-2023-uci-world-champs-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtail-shimano-xtr-drivetrain-10-45-short-cage-derailleur-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcok-pro-bike-check-2023-uci-world-champs-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtail-shimano-xtr-drivetrain-10-45-short-cage-derailleur-200x300.jpg 200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcok-pro-bike-check-2023-uci-world-champs-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtail-shimano-xtr-drivetrain-10-45-short-cage-derailleur-80x120.jpg 80w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcok-pro-