pg?strip=info&amp;w=1600&amp;ssl=1 1600w\" alt src=\"https://i1.wp.com/bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/pidcock-pinarello-dogma-xc-ht-pro-bike-check-most-ultra-talo-xc-handlebar-800x534.jpg?ssl=1\" /></figure><figure><img srcset=\"https://i1.wp.com/bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/pidcock-pinarello-dogma-xc-ht-pro-bike-check-shiamno-xtr-brakes-2-piston-calipers-800x534.jpg?strip=info&amp;w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i1.wp.com/bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/pidcock-pinarello-dogma-xc-ht-pro-bike-check-shiamno-xtr-brakes-2-piston-calipers-800x534.jpg?strip=info&amp;w=900&amp;ssl=1 900w, https://i1.wp.com/bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/pidcock-pinarello-dogma-xc-ht-pro-bike-check-shiamno-xtr-brakes-2-piston-calipers-800x534.jpg?strip=info&amp;w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w, https://i1.wp.com/bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/pidcock-pinarello-dogma-xc-ht-pro-bike-check-shiamno-xtr-brakes-2-piston-calipers-800x534.jpg?strip=info&amp;w=1500&amp;ssl=1 1500w, https://i1.wp.com/bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/pidcock-pinarello-dogma-xc-ht-pro-bike-check-shiamno-xtr-brakes-2-piston-calipers-800x534.jpg?strip=info&amp;w=1600&amp;ssl=1 1600w\" alt src=\"https://i1.wp.com/bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/pidcock-pinarello-dogma-xc-ht-pro-bike-check-shiamno-xtr-brakes-2-piston-calipers-800x534.jpg?ssl=1\" /></figure></div></div><div><div><figure><img srcset=\"https://i2.wp.com/bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcock-pinarello-xc-hardtail-mtb-pro-bike-check-shimano-xtr-brakes-160mm-ice-tech-freeza-rotors-800x534.jpg?strip=info&amp;w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i2.wp.com/bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcock-pinarello-xc-hardtail-mtb-pro-bike-check-shimano-xtr-brakes-160mm-ice-tech-freeza-rotors-800x534.jpg?strip=info&amp;w=900&amp;ssl=1 900w, https://i2.wp.com/bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcock-pinarello-xc-hardtail-mtb-pro-bike-check-shimano-xtr-brakes-160mm-ice-tech-freeza-rotors-