-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/pidcock-pinarello-dogma-xc-full-suspension-pro-bike-check-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/pidcock-pinarello-dogma-xc-full-suspension-pro-bike-check-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/pidcock-pinarello-dogma-xc-full-suspension-pro-bike-check.jpg 1600w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcock-pinarello-dogma-full-suspension-cross-country-bike-with-prototype-continental-ruban-tread-pattern.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"534\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcock-pinarello-dogma-full-suspension-cross-country-bike-with-prototype-continental-ruban-tread-pattern-800x534.jpg\" alt srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcock-pinarello-dogma-full-suspension-cross-country-bike-with-prototype-continental-ruban-tread-pattern-800x534.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcock-pinarello-dogma-full-suspension-cross-country-bike-with-prototype-continental-ruban-tread-pattern-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcock-pinarello-dogma-full-suspension-cross-country-bike-with-prototype-continental-ruban-tread-pattern-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcock-pinarello-dogma-full-suspension-cross-country-bike-with-prototype-continental-ruban-tread-pattern-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcock-pinarello-dogma-full-suspension-cross-country-bike-with-prototype-continental-ruban-tread-pattern-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcock-pinarello-dogma-full-suspension-cross-country-bike-with-prototype-continental-ruban-tread-pattern-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tom-pidcock-pinarello-dogma-full-suspension-cross-country-bike-with-prototype-continental-ruban-tread-pattern.jpg 1600w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>With alternating blocks of the center tread pattern cut down, the tire is likely better able to bite into the soft terrain the riders have been dealing with on track this week.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Good luck to Tom and the rest of the INEOS team this weekend!</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://pinarello.com/\" target=\"_blank\">pinarello.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/tom-pidcocks-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtail-pro-bike-check/\">Pro Bike Check: Tom Pidcock’s Pinarello Dogma XC HT Short Track Bike</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Jessie-May Morgan","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"80c87ce376e75ae5f8273529be6434b057bf5232079663ea1fa9ee9ed49f3c0c","category":"Cycling"}